287
00:23:26,830 --> 00:23:30,900
Well, he was sharing his thoughts with us.

288
00:23:30,900 --> 00:23:33,090
It's one of the two.

289
00:23:33,090 --> 00:23:36,490
Either you empathized with the manager's feelings

