00:23:51,660 --> 00:23:53,190
Yes.

295
00:24:06,050 --> 00:24:09,760
Thank you for the ride. Go home safe.

296
00:24:09,760 --> 00:24:11,160
Okay.

297
00:24:17,500 --> 00:24:19,770
Yeon Hwa...

