354
00:28:31,890 --> 00:28:35,710
Move your tent. This is a parking lot.

355
00:28:36,880 --> 00:28:40,380
I'm sorry. It was tough to set it up.

356
00:28:41,390 --> 00:28:44,060
- Help me.
- Careful.

357
00:28:49,050 --> 00:28:51,390
That sounds great.

358
00:28:53,410 --> 00:28:56,290
Oh? Wait!

359
00:28:57,840 --> 00:29:00,860
- CEO!
- Yeon Hwa!

360
00:29:04,520 --> 00:29:06,730
- Hello.
- Wow.

361
00:29:06,730 --> 00:29:09,310
It's great to see you guys like this.

362
00:29:09,310 --> 00:29:12,110
Why did you lose so much weight?

363
00:29:12,110 --> 00:29:14,340
How have you been?

364
00:29:14,340 --> 00:29:17,060
Just taking a break, you know.

365
00:29:18,740 --> 00:29:21,760
- Newbie, aren't we going?
- Coming.

366
00:29:21,760 --> 00:29:23,670
- Do you want something to drink?
- What?

367
00:29:23,670 --> 00:29:25,340
- Iced Americano for me.
- Iced carmel macchiato.

368
00:29:34,190 --> 00:29:37,440
Geez, he's so mean.

369
00:29:42,910 --> 00:29:48,270
What can you do? Geez, I had no idea he'd be like that.

370
00:29:48,970 --> 00:29:51,230
But you know...

371
00:29:51,230 --> 00:29:54,510
- Curious about who he is?
- Yes.

372
00:29:54,510 --> 00:29:58,580
It's Jo Tae Goo. He was the former CEO of Joybuster.

373
00:29:58,580 --> 00:30:02,120
