- We fired him.

374
00:30:02,120 --> 00:30:04,020
But why would be come here?

375
00:30:04,020 --> 00:30:09,130
He sold off all his shares and kept only one share. Only one.

376
00:30:09,130 --> 00:30:15,320
But the problem is he has the right to attend the shareholders meeting with that one share.

377
00:30:16,700 --> 00:30:20,600
Seeing the way he is, I think he came to ruin the shareholders meeting.

378
00:30:22,280 --> 00:30:25,320
I wondered why it was so easy to get rid of him.

379
00:30:33,860 --> 00:30:35,790
- Have some.
- Here you go.

380
00:30:37,300 --> 00:30:38,950
Thank you!

381
00:30:38,950 --> 00:30:40,410
Oh, Soo Jung.

382
00:30:40,410 --> 00:30:41,420
