385
00:30:44,980 --> 00:30:46,880
Why didn't you invite me? I'm sad.

386
00:30:46,880 --> 00:30:51,090
How can I? It was the day after you got fired.

387
00:30:51,090 --> 00:30:53,540
I would've still gone crying.

388
00:30:54,710 --> 00:30:56,430
Thank you.

389
00:30:56,430 --> 00:30:59,970
I'm ashamed of coming here like this.

390
00:30:59,970 --> 00:31:02,260
I feel so bad toward you all.

391
00:31:02,260 --> 00:31:06,150
Oh, no. Don't say that. There's no other CEO like you.

392
00:31:06,150 --> 00:31:09,930
We feel bad for staying behind.

393
00:31:10,970 --> 00:31:13,560
It would've worked out if we held out a little longer.

394
00:31:14,160 --> 00:31:16,500
I had no power.

395
00:31:16,500 --> 00:31:20,010
You need more strength. Eat meat. It's burning.

396
00:31:20,010 --> 00:31:22,120
